CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 22, 1941, pg. 16 reads: "Centre Avenue 'Y' Little Five - One of the outstanding young basketball teams in Pittsburgh is the Centre Avenue 'Y' Little Five, pictured above. Coached by Pomeroyal Fountain this team will some day represent the Centre Avenue institution as its major team. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of twelve Centre Avenue "Y Little Five" basketball players with two coaches on each end, including Pomeroyal Fountain on left, posed in interior, possibly Centre Avenue YMCA
